data.title: Speech by Gamal Abdel Nasser on the nationalisation of the Suez Canal Company (26 July 1956)
meta_keywords: speech by gamal abdel nasser on the nationalisation of the suez canal company (26 july 1956)
data.meta_description: On 26 July 1956, Egyptian President Gamal Abdel Nasser delivers a speech in Alexandria in which he announces the nationalisation of the Suez Canal Company.
